N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 332.9 - Filing of notice

State Regulations

All notices required to be filed with the chair pursuant to
this Subchapter shall be deemed filed when received by the Chair, Workers'
Compensation Board, 180 Livingston Street, Brooklyn, NY
11248. Notes
